info.header: RSLTE033 - VLAN analysis per QoS class
info.help_text:
This report shows VLAN performance of traffic per per hope behaviour. The report is sub-divided in the following groups:
- total volume for vlan;
- total outbound data volume per hope behaviour (from class 4 to best effort);
- total inbound data volume per hope behaviour (from class 4 to best effort);
- received vlan interface packets per hope behaviour (from class 4 to best effort);
- average outbound data rate per hope behaviour (from class 4 to best effort);
- average inbound data rate per hope behaviour (from class 4 to best effort);
